<!-- AI 여행 계획 -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI와 함께 여행 계획을 세워보세요</h2>
<p class="text-gray-600">몇 가지 질문에 답하면 AI가 당신에게 맞는 여행 코스를 추천해 드립니다</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">여행 스타일 선택</h3>
<div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
<label class="custom-checkbox block text-gray-700">
<input type="checkbox">
<span class="checkmark"></span>
